<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Resource_item_arm  Entity: Resource_group_relationship  
   <express_ref linkend="resource_item:arm:Resource_item_arm.Resource_group_relationship"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Resource_item_arm.Resource_group_relationship">
A <b>Resource_group_relationship</b> links a relating resource group to a related resource item that is part of the resource group. The meaning of
the entity is determined by classification.
<note number="1">
The relationship between a tool set and a malet could be classified as "Contains".
</note>
<note number="2">
The relationship between a facility and compressed air could be classified as "Provides".
</note>
</ext_description>
